    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand on the \"marketplace of ideas\" part? I want to dive deeper into how the government's attempt to moderate content—like preventing misinformation or hate speech—actually destroys the integrity of that marketplace by picking winners and losers.",
